        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="https://richmond.craigslist.org/apa/d/richmond-3-with-split-layout-so-you-can/7517269296.html"></div>
        </div>
A 3/2 with a split layout so you can have ample privacy from rest of family. Featuring stainless steel appliances, large double-hung windows that can open from top to bottom, a bright kitchen with a skylight, modern zebra blinds in each room, a security system, and gorgeous crown molding throughout. There is a large front porch with recessed lED lighting for those cool summer nights. A 2-car driveway was recently added (another rarity). It is very convenient to take advantage of the best Richmond has to offer. House is a must see!!<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
