Hi there<br>
<br>
I am looking for unfurnished room to rent for my massage and body healing business. my budget is $700 a month. I have a massage business, so some clients come over for treatments and go.<br>
I am looking for private room with shower and nice nature surroundings.<br>
Mid thirties couple who doesn't party or cause trouble seeking 2 bedroom with budget of about 2000<br>
We have 2 small French bulldogs and 1 small English bulldog<br>
We have never missed a rent payment but our credit is not great because I was laid off my last job and spend of rent first<br>
I now have a new great job and ready to catch up<br>
